title: China, U.S. reach some deals in trade, differences remain
text:
China, U.S. reach some deals in trade, differences remain 7:37pm IST - 01:47
Top officials from China and the United States have reached a consensus on some aspects of the countries' trade row, but disagreements over other issues remain ''relatively big'', according to China's Xinhua news agency. Ciara Lee reports.
